  traits:
  - 'Frail broken body, tattered useless wings

    held aloft by white-masked acolytes.'
  - 'Sees the potential failures of those who

    ask for advice. Has no faith in
    anybody to

    succeed at any task.'
  - Wants to bask in vicarious glory.
